Package it.polimi.ingsw.net

Class ClientDispatcher

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.net.ClientDispatcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientDispatcherInterface
public class ClientDispatcher extends Object implements ClientDispatcherInterface
The `ClientDispatcher` class implements the `ClientDispatcherInterface` interface and is responsible for dispatching messages received from the server to the corresponding client. Each `dispatch` method receives a specific type of message and forwards it to the client by calling the corresponding methods in the `ClientInterface`.
Author:
Tommaso Trabacchin, Melanie Tonarelli, Emanuele Valsecchi, Adem Shehi
